issue.title: Fix images
issue.body:
Fixes image fetching for politician avatars in most cases. Please note:
- If the Google Civic API has an invalid FB page URL then the image loading fails. `Avatar` (DS component) needs a fallback image prop. (@lachlanjc)
- Twitter URLs (for image fetching) have been disabled because they Just Don't Work:tm: 
- This is bad code
